data.description: LOOKING FOR A ONE LEVEL ALL BRICK BEAUTY? Check out this Charming 2BR/1BA home nestled in the heart Thomasville. Rocking chair front porch, Spacious rooms, Formal dining room, Tons of cabinet space in the gala styled kitchen w/ Gas Stove. Refrigerator remains. Some Updates include: 2023 New Shower installed, 2022 LVP flooring in Kitchen, 2021 Roof on Home and Out Buildings, Newer vinyl windows. Gas log fireplace in Living Room, Gas water heater. The home sits on .51 acre and is close to shopping and restaurants. The house also has a spacious backyard perfect for entertaining along with two prewired storage buildings, (28'x24' & 18'x12') perfect for storage and/or workshops. Come take a look and see all that this house has to offer! Being sold "AS IS".
